definition: small craftsman (contemptuous)/clatter (e.g. of footsteps)/jumbled mass/press of bodies/tumult
classifier for sheets of papers etc: pile, pad/Taiwan pr. [ta4]

sentences.english: No extraordinary disorder hinstanceens on the orderly circumference.
sentences.chinese: 在有序的界線上沒有發作不尋常的雜沓。

sentences.english: With a clatter, the flatterer shattered the chattering wattmeter in the chaos.
sentences.chinese: 賣啷一聲，馬屁精在雜沓中打碎了格格作響的瓦特表。

sentences.english: There were crashing footsteps in the brush now.
sentences.chinese: 現在叢樹林裏響起了雜沓的腳步聲。
